    {
      "id": "h38QyMQAxabWp7d9wyLQt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 792.7259216308594,
      "y": 428.29998779296875,
      "width": 810.9994506835938,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 376177174,
      "version": 163,
      "versionNonce": 990493846,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776852958472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This is bad - we have to do all the permutation and combination classes hence its \nbad remember always inheritance is bad, it creates class explosion ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "This is bad - we have to do all the permutation and combination classes hence its \nbad remember always inheritance is bad, it creates class explosion ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Z9HBilbhKbFyMgG2E_oun",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 806.7259216308594,
      "y": 510.29998779296875,
      "width": 512.0196533203125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1033063114,
      "version": 60,
      "versionNonce": 347332874,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776852978203,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We cant code reuse here, it breaks the DRY principle",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We cant code reuse here, it breaks the DRY principle",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2dZn_l9IYESoiOKK5C3MY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 245.72592163085938,
      "y": 672.8053013042602,
      "width": 1151.7063133305255,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 773297814,
      "version": 275,
      "versionNonce": 1093951686,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781345602767,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Bridge :- Imagine a concept ( class, problem ) we need to break it to highlevel and low level part, high level is\nabstaction (dikhta kaisa hai), low level (implementation)\nthis is theory tital,  ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Bridge :- Imagine a concept ( class, problem ) we need to break it to highlevel and low level part, high level is abstaction (dikhta kaisa hai), low level (implementation)\nthis is theory tital,  ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zUR0yOGslHBNIfbVir6mK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 292.7259216308594,
      "y": 749.2999877929688,
      "width": 1291.5592041015625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1041403594,
      "version": 226,
      "versionNonce": 609196630,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776853105198,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now we can make our own absteractions and our own implementations, eg. high level ( abstraction ) is our carType like suv,seden etc\nwhile low level (impl) is Engine electric, petrol diesel etc...",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now we can make our own absteractions and our own implementations, eg. high level ( abstraction ) is our carType like suv,seden etc\nwhile low level (impl) is Engine electric, petrol diesel etc...",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pQfpgmX1XVTDBrOW_rr3P",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 366.7259216308594,
      "y": 850.2999877929688,
      "width": 1530.319091796875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1500569354,
      "version": 191,
      "versionNonce": 1352550794,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776853178563,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We talked ki inheritance is bad and composition is good, hence here we say that highlevel has a low level  menas high to low has a relation ship - composition",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We talked ki inheritance is bad and composition is good, hence here we say that highlevel has a low level  menas high to low has a relation ship - composition",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
